<div class="container my-5">
  <h1 class="text-maroon border-bottom pb-2 mb-4">Audition Information</h1>
  
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <p class="lead">Join the Voice of Aggieland. Auditions for the Singing Cadets are held at the beginning of the Fall and Spring semesters.</p>

      <% if @audition_sessions.any? %>
        <% @audition_sessions.each do |session| %>
          <h3 class="mt-5 mb-3"><%= session.label %> Auditions</h3>
          <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-4 border-start border-maroon border-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
                <li class="mb-2">
                  <i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  <strong>Start:</strong> <%= session.start_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p") %>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  <strong>End:</strong> <%= session.end_datetime.strftime("%B %-d, %Y at %-I:%M %p") %>
                </li>
                <li class="mt-2">
                  <i class="bi bi-geo-alt me-2 text-maroon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  <strong>Location:</strong> <%= session.location %>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      <% else %>
        <p class="text-muted mt-4">Audition dates have not been announced yet. Check back soon!</p>
      <% end %>

      <h3 class="mt-4 mb-3">What to Expect</h3>
      <p>The audition process is straightforward. No prepared piece is necessary. The director will guide you through simple vocal exercises to determine your range and pitch matching ability.</p>
      
      <div class="alert bg-light border mt-4">
        <h5 class="alert-heading"><i class="bi bi-question-circle me-2" aria-hidden="true"></i> Do I need to be a music major?</h5>
        <p class="mb-0">No! The Singing Cadets represent almost every major at Texas A&M. A passion for music and dedication to the group are what matter most.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
